<main class="container">

<section class="legal-page">

<h1>LaunchTrack Support</h1>

<p>
  Need help with LaunchTrack? Find answers to common questions below.
</p>


<h2>What is LaunchTrack?</h2>

<p>
  LaunchTrack helps you discover upcoming and past rocket launches,
  including mission details, launch schedules, and related videos.
</p>


<h2>Why is a launch date different from another source?</h2>

<p>
  Launch dates can change frequently due to weather, technical issues,
  or decisions made by launch providers. LaunchTrack displays the
  latest available information from its data sources.
</p>


<h2>Why can't I watch a launch video?</h2>

<p>
  LaunchTrack uses YouTube videos provided by third-party channels.
  A video may become unavailable if it is removed, made private,
  or restricted by the original uploader.
</p>


<h2>The app is showing incorrect information</h2>

<p>
  If you notice incorrect launch information, please contact us with
  the mission name and details so we can investigate.
</p>


<h2>Contact Support</h2>

<p>
  For questions, feedback, or bug reports:
</p>

<a href="mailto:your-email@example.com">
  Contact LaunchTrack Support
</a>


</section>

</main>

</body>

</html>